Thomas is an economist, researcher and activists, his focus is on the role of money in social change. Using several years of experience in international development cooperation mainly in Asia, his core field of work is  now the design and development of  projects which build on the potential of the commons and finance commons. He lives in Berlin and is engaged in various initiatives for sustainable economies and social change.

